    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Attached are copies of a letter recently forwarded to this office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "by the Director of Special Investigations, Alaskan Air Command. In",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "addition to the address in captioned subject, the letter reflects a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "return address of the 18th Cml. Tech. Intel. Det., 100th Cml. Grp.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Fort McClellan, Alabama.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "The original letter was furnished by Major William H. Greenhalgh,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Jr., Commander, 5004th Air Intelligence Service Squadron, Elmendorf",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "AFB, APO 942, Seattle, Washington. Major Greenhalgh advised that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "letter was turned over to Flight A of his organization by Doctor Kennidy,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "DDS, Nome, Alaska. Major Greenhalgh identified Dr. Kennidy as a private",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "pilot who has in the past been the source of several reports to this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "organization. Dr. Kennidy reported that the letter was found in a book",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "which he had loaned to Mr. Small over a year ago and which was recently",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "returned.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
